 <br>
The destination is to become as we are,Shintou-ones who understand that the world truly works as it does. If one wishes to slough off the dedication of themselves to the gods of light,they must willingly sacrifice everything to do so.<br>
<br>
To live a life undedicated to the dark powers is to always have the chance of turning away from them.<br>
 <br>
There is no turning away for us,short of the total sacrifice of our mortal souls in order to become something truly different. Devote yourself or deny yourself the truth in your soul.<br>
 <br>
Corruption is the comfortable middle of the road-both for lightlover and servant of the dark alike. It's so much easier to live that way...though they should wonder about what comes later.<br>
 <br>
There are many corrupted folk that wander Nektulos,their bones chattering still. Some claimed to follow the dark. Others the light.<br>
 <br>
In the end,they are all called to be judged by what they followed.<br>
<br>
<br>
